* D slightly ignored the hand which Fenox placed on his shoulder, not really 
wanting to think about his dead friends.
He watched as she agreed to lead him into the base, watching her form as it 
moved towards the Iron Fist.
He heaved a wolven sigh before following her, tramping over the bridge and 
walking up to her. Ready to go inside when she was.*
